<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Осторожно, контент</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            background: #ffffff;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 90vw;
        }
        .main-text {
            color: #cc0000;
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 10vw, 4.5rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.2;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }
        .subtext {
            color: #222;
            font-size: clamp(0.7rem, 4vw, 1.1rem);
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            display: inline-block;
            padding-top: 0.8rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="main-text">
            ТЫ ШО ДОЛБАЕБ<br>
            ПО НЕЗНАКОМЫМ КЬЮАРАМ<br>
            ПЕРЕХОДИТЬ
        </div>
        <div class="subtext">
            великий адъютант
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
